		<label>Rumrunner</label>
		<description>An old flatbed truck.\nCarries up to 800 kg of cargo and 2 passengers.\n\n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;Crew:&lt;/color&gt; Driver x1, Passenger x1\n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;Fuel type:&lt;/color&gt; Chemfuel</description>

